headline: Investors Still Interested in US, JPM's Crawford Says
summary: JPMorgan Asset Management's Kim Crawford discusses investors' positioning and says that there is "some discontent" on US policy and "some diversification is being embraced." She adds, however, that ultimately investors still want to be in the US given the breath, depth and size of the US Treasury market.
